name: PEPE UWU
description: Pepe UWU ($CUTE) is a digital asset in the form of a meme token, designed to encapsulate and spread themes of kindness and charm within the crypto community. It draws inspiration from the iconic Pepe meme, infusing it with an "UWU" essence, a term often associated with cuteness and endearing emotions in internet culture. The token primarily serves as a playful and lighthearted addition to the world of digital currencies, emphasizing its role as a symbol of positivity and fun.
